<MELItem itemNbr="52-36-01" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-52-36-01.1.2-52-36-01">
<Title>Bulk Cargo Door Gas Spring</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Bulk cargo door damper operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Safety hold open device is used when door is in the open position.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Note>
<Para>The bulk cargo door is heavy and may require two people when opening.</Para>
</Note>
<Para>When the bulk cargo door is opened, secure the door in the open position with the safety strap loop installed in the bulk compartment (AMM DDG 52-36-01).</Para>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
